fields.name: BP_Monthly_Volume_Visa_MC_DS__c
fields.label: Monthly Volume (Visa/MC/DS)
fields.info_tooltip: Monthly credit card volume is the combined dollar amount of Visa, MasterCard and Discover sales your business typically processes on a monthly basis.

fields.name: BP_Average_Ticket_Visa_MC_DS__c
fields.label: Average Ticket (Visa/MC/DS)
fields.info_tooltip: The average ticket is the average dollar amount your customer spends on any given sale using a Visa, MasterCard or Discover card for payment.

fields.name: BP_Highest_ticket_Visa_MC_DS__c
fields.label: Highest ticket (Visa/MC/DS)
fields.info_tooltip: The highest ticket is the most the merchant's customer has spent on a single purchase using a Visa, MasterCard or Discover card for payment.

fields.name: BP_Monthly_Volume_AMEX__c

fields.name: SD_Upload_Voided_Check__c
fields.label: Upload Voided Check or Bank Letter
fields.info_tooltip: Voided checks from the bank account where deposits will be made and fees will be deducted. Check must be valid, display bank name, business name and business address. If not available, provide signed bank letter (on bank letterhead) which includes bank account, routing number(s) and business name.

fields.name: SD_Upload_Physical_Address__c
fields.label: Upload Proof of Physical Address
fields.info_tooltip: Required for RETAIL merchants: Provide a utility bill, sales tax license, business license, processing statements or other official document showing the location's declared physical address as listed on the merchant agreement. CANNOT BE A PO BOX. MUST BE A PHYSICAL ADDRESS. Required for Internet/MOTO merchants: Provide website URL.

fields.name: SD_Upload_Tax_ID__c
fields.label: Upload Proof of EIN/FED Tax ID
fields.info_tooltip: An official (IRS- SS-4) document showing a match between legal name, and EIN/FED Tax ID Number.

fields.name: SD_Upload_Government_ID__c
fields.label: Copy of Government Issued ID
fields.info_tooltip: For verification purposes we will need a valid government issued ID number.  Acceptable forms of a government ID are a driver's license, passport,  U.S. military ID (active duty or retired military and their dependents, and DoD civilians) and permanent resident card.
